{
  "texts": [
    "We show the quantitative relationships of these terms in Fig. 1, averaged over 100 simulations.",
    "The chosen parameter settings are intended for the ground experiments (see Table 1).",
    "The 'lensing residual' denotes to ⟨B del S,ℓm B del * S,ℓm ⟩, which quantifies the remaining lensing signal after delensing.",
    "The 'Bias terms due to noise' represents the total of ⟨B del N,ℓm B del * N,ℓm ⟩, ⟨B del S,ℓm B del * N,ℓm ⟩, ⟨B del S,ℓm B noise * ℓm ⟩ and ⟨B del N,ℓm B noise * ℓm⟩, which we believe quantifies the effects caused by the instrumental noise and reconstruction noise.",
    "The 'total bias terms' are the sum of the previous two."
  ]
}